### Health test through Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/health-test


### Get all recommendations for Paris
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations?destination=Paris


### Get Paris attractions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/attractions?destination=Paris


### Get Paris hotels under budget
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/hotels?destination=Paris&budget=100


### Save recommendation with id 1 for trip 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/1/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripId": 1,
  "userId": "demo-user"
}


### Get saved recommendations for trip 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/saved?tripId=1


### Estimate trip cost from saved recommendations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/estimate?tripId=1